ed="T" n="0841c10"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0841c10"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>吳郡<persName key="A012755">義師</persName>傳（<persName key="A012758">證智</persName> <persName key="A019453">薦福寺老僧</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0841c11"/><persName key="A012755">釋義師</persName>者，不知何許人也。狀類風狂，語言<lb
ed="T" n="0841c12"/>倒亂。<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242009652" notAfter-iso="+0790-02-20"><name>貞元</name>初</date>，巡<placeName key="PL000000008352">吳苑</placeName>乞丐，事多先覺，人以<lb
ed="T" n="0841c13"/>此疑之。市肆中百姓屋數間，<persName key="A012755">義師</persName>輒操斧<lb
ed="T" n="0841c14"/>斫劑其簷，禁之不止。其人素知<persName key="A012755">其</persName>神異，禮<lb
ed="T" n="0841c15"/>白之曰：「弟子藉此生活，無壞我屋。」迴顧曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0841c16"/>「汝惜乎？」投斧而去。其夜市火連<anchor xml:id="beg0841003"/>延<anchor xml:id="end0841003"/>而燎，唯<lb
ed="T" n="0841c17"/>所截簷屋數間存焉。好止廢寺中，無冬夏<lb
ed="T" n="0841c18"/>常積聚壞<anchor xml:id="beg0841004"/>旙<anchor xml:id="end0841004"/>蓋、木佛像，悉代薪炭。又於煨<lb
ed="T" n="0841c19"/>火燒炙鯉魚，而多跳躍，灰坌彌漫。撫掌大<lb
ed="T" n="0841c20"/>笑，不具<anchor xml:id="beg0841sgsz11"/>匕<anchor xml:id="end0841sgsz11"/>筯而食。面垢不<anchor xml:id="beg0841sgsz13"/>靧<anchor xml:id="end0841sgsz13"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0841sgsz15"/>靧<anchor xml:id="end0841sgsz15"/>之輒陰<lb
ed="T" n="0841c21"/>雨，<placeName key="PL000000008352">吳</placeName>人以為占候。及將死也，飲灰汁數十<lb
ed="T" n="0841c22"/>斛，乃念佛而坐，士庶觀之，滿七日而死。時<lb
ed="T" n="0841c23"/>盛暑，色不變，支不摧。百姓<anchor xml:id="beg0841sgsz17"/>舁<anchor xml:id="end0841sgsz17"/>出郊外焚之。<lb
ed="T" n="0841c24"/>又<placeName key="PL000000042180">京兆安國寺</placeName>僧事迹不常，熟地而燒木<lb
ed="T" n="0841c25"/>佛。所言人事，必無虛發。此亦不測之僧也。<lb
ed="T" n="0841c26"/>復次<placeName key="PL000000042258">京師永壽寺</placeName><persName key="A012758">釋証智</persName>，不詳生族。<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242015139" notAfter-iso="+0805-02-28"><name>貞元</name>中</date><lb
ed="T" n="0841c27"/>於<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>寺多發神異，而眾罔知。或晝在<placeName key="PL000000044365">張瀆<lb
ed="T" n="0841c28"/>蘭若</placeName>治田，夜歸寺中。其<placeName key="PL000000044365">蘭若</placeName>在漢陰<placeName key="PL000000044376">金州</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0841c29"/>相距<placeName key="PL000000042189">京甸</placeName>七百里焉。時號<persName key="A012758">智禪師</persName>，此之<persName key="A005672">長<pb ed="T" n="0842a" xml:id="T50.2061.0842a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0842a01"/>足安</persName>、<persName key="A011670">法雲公</persName>也，皆能致遠於瞬息間，道家謂<lb
ed="T" n="0842a02"/>之縮地脈而能陟遐矣。若於色塵作神變，<lb
ed="T" n="0842a03"/>雖遠而近也。次<placeName key="PL000000042270">薦福寺</placeName><persName key="A019453">老僧</persName>，專務誦持，罕<lb
ed="T" n="0842a04"/>有間缺，言未兆事，來如目擊。<date notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922024000" notAfter-iso="+0829-06-03">大和初</date>，相國<lb
ed="T" n="0842a05"/><persName key="A010476">韋公處厚</persName>好重空門，逐月別召名德僧食。<lb
ed="T" n="0842a06"/><persName key="A019453">老僧</persName>見<persName key="A010476">韋</persName>新登庸，曰：「大奇，<persName key="A010476">相公</persName>得如此好<lb
ed="T" n="0842a07"/>滅度處。」人皆不喻，後因奏對於<persName key="A004169">文宗</persName>御前，<lb
ed="T" n="0842a08"/>疾作，僵仆殿階，及扶<anchor xml:id="beg0842sgsz1"/>舁<anchor xml:id="end0842sgsz1"/>出殿<anchor xml:id="beg0842001"/>前<anchor xml:id="end0842001"/>，氣已絕矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0842a09"/>方驗<persName key="A019453">老僧</persName>言，死在內殿中，故云好滅度處。<lb
ed="T" n="0842a10"/>即<date notBefore-iso="+0836-01-26" key="j20264282027904" notAfter-iso="+0840-02-10"><name>開成</name>中</date>也。後不知其終。</p>
